{"tid":778892,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女子買錯機票 在機場大喊：飛機有炸彈！","createTime":"2018-08-14T04:34:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-14T04:39:20.000Z","uid":75969,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e451ee47786289fbad64cff682a8b842f9e3eb24","tid":778892,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T04:34:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180814/_2018081410372782265.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180814%2F_2018081410372782265.jpg&h=1a3a0b62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">謊稱機上有炸彈的那女：「我是讓他們給我們在飛機上找座位。我就想讓飛機不要起飛，給我們解決。」（網圖）<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n累人害己！廣西南寧吳圩國際機場一名女乘客，日前因為自己買錯機票，卻在機場大吵大鬧，而為了阻止航班起飛，竟然向航空公司工作人員聲稱航班上有炸彈。連累機上所有乘客都要落機，重新安檢！航班延誤2個多小時才起飛。而機上確認沒有任何爆炸物威脅，該女子因虛構事實擾亂公共秩序，已被警方處治安拘留5天。<br />\n<br />\n上周五（10日），一名那姓女乘客，原訂從南寧飛往黑龍江哈爾濱，卻錯誤訂購了11日的航班，在機場大堂的售票櫃枱前被拒登機後，大吵大鬧，更坐在地上哭鬧稱航班上有炸彈，警方接報後，立即趕到現場。<br />\n<br />\n那女對謊稱航機有炸彈一事直認不諱，原因是讓航空公司給他們在飛機上找座位，就想讓飛機不要起飛，給他們解決問題。<br />\n<br />\n一位售票處工作人員表示：「我剛才在登機口，她說有炸彈，我就趕緊報警了，現在飛機裏面需要重新清倉檢查。」<br />\n經全面清倉檢查，機場確認飛機上沒有爆炸物威脅，原本已經登機完畢的172名乘客和63件托運行李這才重新回到飛機上，最終導致這趟航班延誤了2個多小時。<br />\n<br />\n目前，該名女乘客因虛構事實擾亂公共秩序，已被警方處以5日治安拘留處罰。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180814/_2018081410400765769.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180814%2F_2018081410400765769.jpg&h=ec202036&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">那女在售票櫃枱前大吵大鬧，坐在地上哭鬧講電話。（網圖）</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/790579\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F790579&d=8wRfes4BNiqzHQc1cLrkttr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=3606441e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F790579&h=9474987a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/790579</a><br />\n<br />\n又自私又無腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d584eaa3bb019ea79dceed6adc34f443e84449a","tid":778892,"uid":30081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T04:35:27.000Z","msg":"Friends <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cc175c7f526975294a246e8bb7fd493b53b901f","tid":778892,"uid":3063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T04:37:47.000Z","msg":"5日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78ee8cdecb22a17d5f3cee18a4f6b61632c653f0","tid":778892,"uid":74442,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T04:39:20.000Z","msg":"根本每位大陸乘客本身就係一個炸彈。鬼叫啲乜"}]}